Dialogue: 0,0:00:02.48,0:00:04.48,Default,narrative,0,0,0,,你好  欢迎光临
Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.48,0:00:06.24,Default,narrative,0,0,0,,你想要奇妙蛋吗？
