Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.20,0:00:11.99,Default,narrative,0,0,0,,什么？你还在犹豫？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.62,0:00:13.91,Default,narrative,0,0,0,,不要犹豫
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.41,0:00:17.33,Default,narrative,0,0,0,,鼓起勇气  相信自己
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.71,0:00:19.62,Default,narrative,0,0,0,,把蛋打破
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.62,0:00:21.21,Default,narrative,0,0,0,,吵死了！
